---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Who is it for" lang="en" description="MEDSEN serves ministries, institutions and operators that run school health. For each: situation, value brought, contracting model.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-sante-600 to-sante-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-white/20 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-5">
          Who is it for
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">
          Three buyers, one solution.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/90">
          For each type of organization: what MEDSEN delivers concretely, and under what model.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ministries -->
  <section id="ministries" class="py-20 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-senegal-green/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-senegal-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 21h18M3 10h18M5 6l7-3 7 3M4 10v11m16-11v11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ministries & governments</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            Ministries of Education, Health, school medical control divisions, school inspectorates.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-senegal-green uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Your situation</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Guaranteeing every child's fundamental rights is part of your sovereign mission,
              within the framework of the Convention on the Rights of the Child. But the lack of
              consolidated data and a shared tool makes that mission hard to deliver at scale.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-senegal-green uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">What MEDSEN brings</div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-senegal-green font-bold">→</span> Nationwide coverage through a single cloud platform.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-senegal-green font-bold">→</span> Real-time consolidated indicators by region, district and school.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-senegal-green font-bold">→</span> Configurable reference data: school cycles, national EPI, tracked conditions.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-senegal-green font-bold">→</span> Compliant with data protection and public procurement rules.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-senegal-green uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Contracting model</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Multi-year SaaS subscription, support and field-team training.
              Adaptable to your public procurement procedures.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Donors -->
  <section id="donors" class="py-20 bg-gray-50 scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Donors & institutions</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            Multilateral institutions, cooperation agencies, funders.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Your situation</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              You fund health or education programs. You need reliable indicators, comparable
              across countries, aligned with SDGs 3 and 4.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">What MEDSEN brings</div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">→</span> Structured exportable reporting, ready-to-use SDG indicators.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">→</span> Cross-country comparability via a common core.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">→</span> Full traceability of funded field actions.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">→</span> Open APIs to integrate with your monitoring systems.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Contracting model</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Co-funding of national rollouts, or full coverage of a country program within
              a regional initiative.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NGOs -->
  <section id="ngos" class="py-20 bg-white scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M9 12a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">NGOs & school networks</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
            International NGOs, private school networks, faith-based institutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-6">
          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Your situation</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              You run several schools and need to professionalize health monitoring while
              meeting your donors' reporting requirements.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">What MEDSEN brings</div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">→</span> Dedicated multi-site tenant, full data isolation.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">→</span> Daily operational tracking of consultations and campaigns.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">→</span> Automated reports in the format your donors expect.</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">→</span> Pricing scaled to network size.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-purple-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Contracting model</div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              SaaS subscription per school, with progressive rollout possible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-sante-600">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Your case isn't listed? Let's talk.
      </h2>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-sante-600 hover:bg-gray-100 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-colors">
        Contact us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
